    },
    "body": "Invalid public keys were accepted in Musig2 partial signatures. Because we serialize invalid keys as the empty byte string, this would lead us to creating an invalid PSBT serializations.\r\n\r\nThis can be checked by reverting the first commit with the fix and simply running the target against the existing qa-assets corpus for the `psbt` harness.",
